history.content: Do you care about mental health issues for college students? Do you have an entrepreneurial mindset willing to do a startup from 0 to 1? Hoping to become a developer, a UI/UX designer, a psychologist, or an entrepreneur? Yes! Excited? Please go check out Re:treat https://www.re-treat.app/about.html: a Skydeck incubated Startup focusing on innovatively solving mental health issues for college students. Our four departments: engineering, content, growth & marketing, and UI/UX design are all recruiting! Looking forward to your applications by the end of Sep 15th. Application form: https://forms.gle/zUupQuHUy35aWNmaA
history.subject: Join Re:Treat to Improve Mental Health on Campus
